data.description: 2.357% VA ASUMABLE LOAN for VETS payments approx. $1,215 on primary Mortgage of $248,750 home sits on TWO separate tax parcels. You be impressed by the beautiful, manicured lawn, fence & attention to detail. Entering the home the vaulted ceilings add dimension to the spacious living room & the large windows let the natural light pour in. The chef will love cooking in this kitchen, there is plenty of counter & cabinet space The two spare bedrooms & guest bath are nice size, the primary suite & bath is a wonderful retreat, the bedroom will accommodate a large bedroom set. Need a separate outdoor studio/office you will love this charming building w/ covered porch, the big level lot is ideal for ADU, it is two legal lots sewer available 2nd lot
